## Notes
- Uses `motion/react` (the `motion` npm package), NOT `framer-motion`. Install `motion`, not `framer-motion`.
- Demo imports from `@/components/blocks/animated-gallery` (not `@/components/ui`). Place the component file in `/components/blocks/` or adjust the import path.
- `@radix-ui/react-slot` and `class-variance-authority` are indirect deps via the shadcn Button component used in the demo.
